query:
SELECT
            lv.id,
            lv.place_id,
            ep.canonical_name as place_name
        FROM data.location_visit lv
        LEFT JOIN data.entities_place ep ON lv.place_id = ep.id
        WHERE lv.start_time <= $2
          AND lv.end_time >= $1
        ORDER BY (lv.end_time - lv.start_time) DESC
        LIMIT 1
